For all the questions about “what is your preferred …”, are you asking about what we have, or what we would most like to have (but don’t necessarily currently have)?

Are you only interested in answers from teams that operate laser cutters, or are you interested in answers from teams that don’t own any laser cutter but would like to own one?

AVHon:

are you asking about what we have, or what we would most like to have (but don’t necessarily currently have)?

If you have a certain brand laser cutter and love it, by all means, put that! It really doesn’t make a huge difference. Just whatever you seem to like the best.

AVHon:

Are you only interested in answers from teams that operate laser cutters, or are you interested in answers from teams that don’t own any laser cutter but would like to own one?

Any and all can answer! It’s not limited to just team members with access to laser cutters. The more answers the better.

I edited the survey to better answer your question.
